locality: Flora of South Africa. C. P. Bredasdorp Div., limestone near Perdekamp.
South Africa. Eastern Cape. Ca. 9 km NNE of Kleinmonde, ca. 3 km N of R72 road. Roy's Vacation Paradise. South Seas Conservation Area, near Cap River.
Waii Nek Mountain, ca. 3 km W of Grahamstown, small mountain overlooking town. On slope among quartzite boulders near edge of windblown summit.
18 km from Grahamstown on King Williamstown road.
Umtamvuna Nature Reserve, E of Mtamvuna River. Hillsides and grasslands above edge of gorge, along path leading away from Visitor Center. Specimens preserved in alcohol.
